                          <td align="Left" valign="CENTER" width="40" bgcolor="#efefef" height="42"><img src="filmljud_small.GIF" width="35" height="32"><a name="mott"></a></td>
                          <td width="610" bgcolor="#efefef" height="42"><b><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font color="#000000"><font size="+1"> 
                            &nbsp;&nbsp;Robert L Mott's Nine Components of Sound</font></font></font></b></td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody> 
                      </table>
                    </center>
                    <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="-1">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font> 
                    &nbsp;<br>
                    <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="-1">Every sound has 
                    its own distinctive wave form.&nbsp;</font></font>&nbsp;<br>
                    <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="-1">Nine components 
                    must be considered to successfully reproduce or create new 
                    sounds.</font></font>&nbsp; <br>
                    &nbsp; 
                    <table border="0" cols="2" width="100%">
                      <tbody> 
                      <tr> 
                        <td><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><b>Musical components</b>:</font> 
