                              Pitch</a>&nbsp;</font></li>
                            <li><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><a href="http://filmsound.studienet.org/articles/ninecomponents/9components.htm#Timbre"> 
                              Timbre</a></font></li>
                            <li><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><a href="http://filmsound.studienet.org/articles/ninecomponents/9components.htm#Harmonics"> 
                              Harmonics</a>(overtones)</font></li>
                            <li><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><a href="http://filmsound.studienet.org/articles/ninecomponents/9components.htm#loudness"> 
                              Loudness</a></font></li>
                            <li><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><a href="http://filmsound.studienet.org/articles/ninecomponents/9components.htm#rhythm"> 
                              Rhythm</a></font></li>
